    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2>Life @ Experion</h2>
                <hr>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>Want to work For Experion?</h3>
                    <p>Experion is a rapidly growing, software product and application development company. During the past decade, we have grown from a 10 member team to a team of 300 and counting. From our initial days at Technopark, Trivandrum, we have grown to have 3 full-fledged software development centers and offices in 7 countries. Our customers include some of the world’s largest corporations as well as some of the sharpest and fastest growing early stage companies.
                        <br>
                        <br> What makes working for Experion truly unique is its culture that encourages innovation, and provides an environment that drives professionals to a challenge themselves helping them grow both professionally and personally.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>What we look for?</h3>
                    <p>We, at Experion, strive to keep a startup culture at our core. The organization has a flat hierarchy and we are constantly on the lookout for the right people to join our team.Apart from good technical and interpersonal skills, we look for people who are
                        <ul>
                            <li>Innovators:- Drivers of innovation, who are ready to take calculated risks.</li>
                            <li>Enterprising:- Roll-up-your-sleeves and let’s get work done mentality.</li>
                            <li>Accountably:- Take responsibility for delivering results without prompting.</li>
                            <li>Proactive:- Not reactive. Always thinking ahead</li>
                            <li>Drive:- The determination to learn new things and get things done.</li>
                            <li> Team Player:- complement other people and be a part of the team.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                    <p>If you fit into this description, email us your resume at <a href="mailto:careers@experionglobal.com" target="_newtab" alt="email">careers@experionglobal.com</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
